			<div class="dablink">This article is about the modern Goidelic language.  For the form of English as it is spoken in Ireland, see <a href="/wiki/Hiberno-English" title="Hiberno-English">Hiberno-English</a>. For the cant based partly on English and partly on Irish, see <a href="/wiki/Shelta" title="Shelta">Shelta</a>.</div>
